---
layout: base.njk
---
<article class="wrap article">
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">홈</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <a href="/blog/">블로그</a>
    <span>/</span>
    <span>{{ title }}</span>
  </nav>

  <header class="article-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">법률 정보</p>
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="description">{{ description }}</p>
    <time datetime="{{ page.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ page.date | readableDate }}</time>
  </header>

  <aside class="notice">
    {{ site.disclaimer }}
  </aside>

  <div class="content">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <section class="contact-band">
    <h2>상담 전 확인할 점</h2>
    <p>채무 규모, 소득, 재산, 압류 여부, 최근 대출 여부를 정리하면 상담이 더 정확해집니다.</p>
    <a class="button" href="/contact/">상담 안내 보기</a>
  </section>
</article>
